 ionship to Earth? This program zooms in on our reliance on Earth and its 
 resources for our lives and well-being. [76 min. total runtime]</p><p><i>
 <strong>There will be a Q&amp\;A following the screening.</strong></i></p
 ><p><i><strong>The River</strong></i><strong>(dir. Temujen Gunawardena\, 
