  environmental crises? This program illustrates our collective concern fo
 r future generations and the choice to be a positive force on Earth. [73 
 min. total runtime]</p><p><i><strong>There will be an awards ceremony fol
 lowing the films.</strong></i></p><p><i><strong>We are Earth</strong></i>
