 ist of activities\, awards\, and work experience  Basic academic informat
 ion (major\, GPA\, expected graduation year)    Staff will be available t
 hroughout the hour to answer questions and help you stay on track. Even i
 f you've never applied for a scholarship before\, this is a great place t
 o start.
