X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Please join the IAUNRC in welcoming Khush Chok
 sy for a lecture on U.S. economic cooperation with Middle Eastern and Cen
 tral Asian nations as part of the "Security Across Central Eurasia in the
  21st Century" series.&#160\;\n</p>
